<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Possible locations (from Arthur from the forum): 
    <ul>

 Apple Lane = Bree 
        <ul>

  Quest: defend Gringle's pawnshop 
        </ul>


 Rainbow Mound = Barrowdowns 
        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Dungeon guardian: Whiteye the Dark Troll and his band of Trollkins 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Other possible quests: 
</p>
</li>

            <ul>

            <li>
<p>
 kill the Great Mother Lizard 
</p>
</li>
            <li>
<p>
 bring the Great Newt back to life 
</p>
</li>

            </ul>        </ul>


 Boldhome = Minas Anor <p>
 Puzzle Canal = Maze 
</p>
<p>
 Snakepipe Hollow = Angband (kill Wakboth) 
</p>
<p>
 Nysalor's Prison = Illusionary Castle 
</p>
<p>
 Under the spike = Mount Doom (Crush X under the spike to destroy it?)    
</p>

    </ul>


<p>
Another possible starting City (from Blackdog): 
</p>

    <ul>

 Pavis and the Big Rubble </ul>

